:: Docks

<<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "docks">><<effects>>
<<skul_dock_init>>

당신은 부두에 있다.
<<if Time.dayState is "dawn">>
	화물을 운송하거나 선적하기 위해 차량들이 도착하면서 벌써부터 분주하게 움직이고 있다.
<<elseif Time.dayState is "day">>
	부두 노동자들이 정박중인 선박에서 작업하느라 바쁘게 움직인다.
<<elseif Time.dayState is "night">>
	밤에는 문을 닫는다. 순찰하는 경비원의 불빛이 쌓여 있는 화물 컨테이너들을 비춘다.
<<elseif Time.dayState is "dusk">>
	마지막 배가 떠나가고, 다른 배들은 밤새 정박해 있다.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if ($docks.askedForWork or $docks.hired) and Time.schoolDay and Time.hour gte 6 and Time.hour lte 8 and $docks.fakeID isnot "shown">>
	당신은 노동자들에게 다가가지만, 매니저가 당신을 막아선다. "미안하지만, 안 된다 소녀야. 너도 규칙을 알겠지: 학생은 주중에 부두에서 일할 수 없다."

	<<if $id is 1>>
		<<set $docks.fakeID to "idea">>
		<br>
		<span class="blue">어쩌면, 그들은 브라이어가 마련해 준 당신의 신분증을 보여주면 주중에도 일하도록 허락해 줄지도 모른다.</span>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

<<if $arousal gte $arousalmax>>
	<<orgasmLocation "docks">>
<</if>>
<<if $docks.hired and Time.schoolDay and Time.hour gte 6 and Time.hour lte 8 and $docks.fakeID is "not considered">>
	Dockers arrive for work. They won't let you join them on a school day.
	<br><br>
<</if>>
<<if $robindebtevent gte 1 and $docksrobinintro isnot 1 and $robinmissing is "docks">>
	<<investigateicon>><<link [[로빈을 찾는다 (0:20)|Docks_Robin]]>><<pass 20>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $docks.askedForWork and !$docks.hired and Time.dayState isnot "night" and $exposed lte 0>>
	<<docksicon>><<link [[일을 구한다 (0:30)|Docks Take Job]]>><<pass 30>><<set $docks.hired to true>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif $docks.hired and Time.hour gte 6 and Time.hour lte 8 and !$daily.docksLeftEarly and $exposed lte 0 and (!Time.schoolDay or $docks.fakeID is "shown")>>
	<<if pcAreArmsBound("both")>>
		<span class="red">Both of your arms are bound</span>, so you are unable to work as a docker.
	<<else>>
		<<if Time.minute is 0>>
			<<set _time_to_display to (16 - Time.hour) + ":00">>
		<<elseif Time.minute >= 51>>
			<<set _time_to_display to (15 - Time.hour) + ":0" + (60 - Time.minute)>>
		<<else>>
			<<set _time_to_display to (15 - Time.hour) + ":" + (60 - Time.minute)>>
		<</if>>

		<<if Time.hour is 6>>
			<<link [["부두 노동자로 일한다 (" + _time_to_display + ")"|Docks Start Early]]>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>> /* started early, phase used in Docks Start */
		<<else>>
			<<link [["부두 노동자로 일한다 (" + _time_to_display + ")"|Docks Start]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>> /* started exactly on time or late, phase used in Docks Start */
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<br>
<<elseif !$docks.askedForWork and !$docks.hired and Time.dayState isnot "night" and $exposed lte 0>>
	<<socialiseicon "ask">><<link [[도울 일이 있는지 묻는다 (0:05)|Docks Ask]]>><<pass 5>><<set $docks.askedForWork to true>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $exposed lte 0 and Time.dayState isnot "night" and $docks.status gte 80 and $docks.wage lt 2500>>
	/* <<dockstatus>> multiplies inputs by 2 and clamps, so asking for a raise is -40 status */
	/* At the earliest fame to ask for a raise, this sets you to 40, and at the highest, 60 */
	<<socialiseicon "ask">><<link [[임금 인상을 요구한다 (0:05)|Docks Raise]]>><<pass 5>><<set $docks.wage += 100>><<dockstatus -20>><</link>><<lllcool>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if Time.dayState is "night">>
	<<sneakicon>><<link [[몰래 들어간다 (0:05)|Docks Sneak Start]]>><<set $bus to "S">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<storeon "docks" "check">>
<<if _store_check is 1>>
	<<dressasyouwereicon>><<link [[옷을 입는다|Docks]]>><<storeon "docks">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $id is 1 and ($docks.askedForWork or $docks.hired) and Time.hour gte 6 and Time.hour lte 8 and $docks.fakeID is "idea">>
	<<ind>><<link [[가짜 신분증을 제시한다 (0:02)|Docks Fake ID]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

<br>
<<mericon>><<link [[떠난다|Mer Street]]>><</link>>
<br>

<<if $debug is 1>>
	<<link [[(debug) 부두 평판 최대|Docks]]>><<set $docks.status to 100>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[(debug) 부두 평판 최소|Docks]]>><<set $docks.status to 0>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Docks Raise
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>
<<generate1>><<person1>>

You ask a manager for a raise. "Well..." <<He>> adjusts <<his>> glasses and taps something into <<his>> computer. "You have been pulling your weight around here. Fine. You're on <span class="gold">£<<print (($docks.wage * 8) / 100)>></span> a shift now, plus <span class="gold">£<<print (($docks.wage / 100) * 1.5)>></span> for every hour of overtime."
<<trauma -18>><<stress -18>><<lltrauma>><<llstress>>
<br><br>

<<if $docks.wage gte 2500>>
	"That's more than any other worker," <<he>> adds.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

The other dockers overheard and grumble as you leave. They're just jealous.
<br><br>

<<endevent>>

<<link [[다음|Docks]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Ask
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>>

당신은 높은 플랫폼에 서 있는 남자에게 다가간다. 그는 노동자들을 관찰하면서 클립보드에 무언가를 적는다.
<br><br>

<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"실례합니다," 당신은 말한다. "귀-귀찮게 해서 죄송합니다. 일자리 있나요?"
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"이봐," 당신은 말한다. "나는 일자리를 찾고 있어. 누구랑 얘기해야 되지?"
<<else>>
	"안녕하세요," 당신은 말한다. "일자리 있나요?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

그는 클립보드에서 고개를 들지 않고, 물가 근처에 더 가까운 작은 건물 쪽을 펜으로 가리킨다.
<br><br>

문이 열려 있다. <<generate2>>한 남자가 책상에서 고개를 들어 당신을 바라본다. "아," 그가 안경을 코 위로 올리며 말한다. "일을 찾고 있습니까?" 당신은 고개를 끄덕인다. 그는 일어서서 책상과 벽 사이를 비집고 당신 앞에 섰다. 그가 손을 내민다.
<br><br>

<<link [[다음|Docks Ask 2]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Ask 2
"우리는 일손이 더 필요합니다," 그가 말한다. "요즘 배가 너무 많이 드나들거든요. 설명이 필요하시겠죠." 그는 책상 뒤에 다시 앉는다.
<br><br>

"<<printmoney 1500>>가 초봉입니다. 실적이 좋다면 더 올려줄 수 있습니다. 부두는 <span class="gold"><<ampm 6 00>></span>에 열리고, 근무는 <span class="gold"><<ampm 7 00>></span>부터 시작합니다. 8시간 교대 근무제로, 당신은 <span class="gold"><<ampm 16 00>></span>까지 일하게 될 겁니다."
<br><br>

<span class="teal">"Y급여를 받으려면 근무 시간 내내 근무해야 합니다."</span>
<br><br>

"만약 당신이 그럴 만한 능력이 된다면, <span class="gold"><<ampm 19 00>></span>까지 근무하고 추가 수당을 받을 수 있습니다. 추가 근무이기 때문에, 기본 수당에 50%를 더 얹어서 시간당 <span class="gold"><<printmoney 2250>></span>를 받게 될 거예요. 언제든 근무를 마칠 수 있고."
<br><br>

"아, 그리고 지각하지 마세요." 그는 덧붙인다. "직원들이 아무 시간대에 출근하게 할 수는 없습니다. 보안상의 이유 때문입니다. 7시부터 8시 사이에 출근하지 않으면 들어올 수 없습니다. 제가 문책받을 수 있으니, 당신이 학교에 가는 주중에는 근무할 수 없고요."
<br><br>

<<if $id is 1>>
	<<set $docks.fakeID to "shown">>
	You show <<him>> the fake ID you purchased from Briar. "I'm not a student<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>..<</if>>."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> glances at it, then hands it back. "Can't be too careful. Everything else still applies, except for the 'no working on school days' part."
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<link [[다음|Docks Ask 3]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Ask 3
그는 당신의 몸을 위아래로 훑어본다.

<<if currentSkillValue('physique') gte 15000>>
	"건장하시군요, 아가씨. 육체적으로 힘든 일이긴 하겠지만, 당신이라면 아무 문제 없을 거예요."
<<elseif currentSkillValue('physique') gte 10000>>
	"건강해 보이네요. 육체적으로 힘든 일이지만, 당신은 괜찮을 겁니다."
<<elseif currentSkillValue('physique') gte 5000>>
	"이건 육체적으로 힘든 일입니다. 잘 할 수 있을 것 같지만, 조심하세요."
<<else>>
	그가 한숨을 쉰다. "이건 육체적으로 힘든 일이고, 그리고, 음." 그는 멈춘다. "당신은 제가 본 것 중에서 가장 강한 소녀는 아닙니다, 그렇게 말하도록 하죠. 당신을 막지는 않겠지만, 고생할지도 모릅니다."
<</if>>
<br><br>

"이게 전부입니다. 기술적 측면에 대한 기본적인 정보를 더 드릴 수 있고, 나머지는 직접 배우면 될 겁니다. 관심 있나요?"
<br><br>

<<link [[네 (0:30)|Docks Take Job]]>><<pass 30>><<set $docks.hired to true>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[아니요|Docks Refuse Job]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Refuse Job
"아쉽네요," 그가 한숨을 쉬었다. "생각이 바뀌면 다시 오세요."
<br><br>

<<endevent>>
<<link [[다음|Docks]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Take Job
<<effects>>

"기억하세요," 매니저가 말한다. "<span class="gold"><<ampm 7 00>></span>까지는 출근해야<<if $docks.fakeID isnot "shown">> 하고, 당신이 학교에 가는 날에는 일할 수 없습니다<</if>> 합니다. 경비원이 당신을 <<ampm 9 00>>까지는 들여보내 주겠지만, 지각을 습관 삼지는 마세요. 근무는 <span class="gold"><<ampm 16 00>></span>에 종료됩니다. 팀에 합류한 것을 환영합니다."
<br><br>

<<link [[다음|Docks]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Docks Start Early
<<effects>>

<<if Time.minute lt 55>>
	당신은 보안을 통과하고 근무 시간이 시작되기를 기다린다. Dockers talk amongst themselves while passing the time.
	<br><br>

	<<if !$docks.firstDay>>
		<<dockoverhear>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	You pass security and join the other dockers. You barely have time to get settled before your shift begins.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<set _time_to_pass to (60 - Time.minute)>>
<<if _time_to_pass is 60>>
	<<set _time_to_display to "1:00">>
<<elseif _time_to_pass lt 10>>
	<<set _time_to_display to "0:0" + _time_to_pass>>
<<else>>
	<<set _time_to_display to "0:" + _time_to_pass>>
<</if>>

<<link [["다음 (" + _time_to_display + ")"|Docks Start]]>><<pass _time_to_pass>><</link>>

:: Docks Start
<<effects>>

<<set $docks.dailyHours.shift.total to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.shift.workedHard to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.shift.slacked to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.shift.unpaid to 0>>
<<set $docks.dailyHours.overtime.total to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.overtime.workedHard to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.overtime.slacked to 0>><<set $docks.dailyHours.overtime.unpaid to 0>>

<<if $docks.firstDay>> /* this is set to false later in this passage */
	당신은 <<if $phase is 1>>보안을 통과하고 <</if>>매니저에게 일을 시작하겠다고 보고한다.
	<br><br>
	"First day on the job?" the <<generate1>><<person1>><<person>> asks. You nod. <<He>> writes something on a clipboard.
	<<if Time.hour is 7 and Time.minute is 0>>
		"And on time at <span class="gold"><<ampm 7 00>></span> sharp. Good. Let's keep it that way."
	<<elseif Time.hour is 7 and Time.minute lt 15>>
		"A little late, but not too bad. Try to be here by <span class="gold"><<ampm 7 00>></span> in the future."
	<<else>>
		"You're late. That's alright, you're fresh from orientation. Try to be here by <span class="gold"><<ampm 7 00>></span> in the future. You won't be paid for any hours you miss."
	<</if>>
<<elseif Time.hour is 7>>
	<<if $phase is 0>> /* arrived early, set in docks passage */
		You report to a manager for work.
	<<elseif Time.minute is 0>>
		You pass security and report to a manager for work.
	<<elseif Time.minute lt 3>>
		You pass security and report to a manager for work. <<generate1>><<person1>><<He>> doesn't seem to care that you're a couple minutes late.
	<<elseif Time.minute lt 15>>
		You pass security and report to a manager for work. <<generate1>><<person1>><<He>> pointedly reminds you to show up on time.<<stress 6>><<gstress>>
	<<elseif Time.minute lt 30>>
		Security stops you and calls a manager to check if you work here. When you're allowed entry, a <<generate1>><<person1>><<person>> scolds you for showing up late.<<stress 6>><<trauma 6>><<gstress>><<gtrauma>>
	<<else>>
		Security stops you and calls a manager to check if you work here. When you're allowed entry, a <<generate1>><<person1>><<person>> harshly scolds you for showing up <<if Time.minute gt 30>>over <</if>>half an hour late.<<stress 12>><<trauma 6>><<ggstress>><<gtrauma>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif Time.hour is 8>>
	Security stops you and calls a manager to check if you work here. When you're allowed entry, a <<generate1>><<person1>><<person>> harshly scolds you in front of the other dockers for showing up <<if Time.minute gt 0>>over <</if>>an hour late.<<stress 12>><<trauma 6>><<dockstatus -1>><<ggstress>><<gtrauma>><<lcool>>
<<else>>
	You shouldn't see this passage! Report this to Vrelnir.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<endevent>>

/* Set the type of workday. First day is always normal */
<<if $docks.firstDay>>
	<<set $docks.dayType to "normal">>
	<<set $docks.firstDay to false>> /* end of first day differences, set early to avoid more complex checks based on leave times */
<<else>>
	<<if $christmas is 1>>
		<<if Time.monthDay is 25>>
			<span class="green">It's Christmas day.</span> A manager thanks the few dockers who are present and says that they will receive overtime rates all day and a <span class="gold">£100</span> bonus at the end of their shift.
		<<else>>
			<span class="lblue">It's the week before Christmas.</span> A manager states that all employees who work this week will receive a <span class="gold">£25</span> bonus at the end of the day.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $rng gte 86>> /* 15% chance */
		<span class="red">The docks are busy today.</span> Work will be tiring. A manager announces that the overtime rate is raised from 150% to 200% for the day.
		<<set $docks.dayType to "busy">>
	<<elseif $rng gte 71>> /* 15% chance */
		<span class="blue">Few ships are coming in today.</span> Work will be easy, but there won't be enough work to stay overtime.
		<<set $docks.dayType to "slow">>
	<<elseif $rng lte Math.floor($world_corruption_soft/5)>> /* 0-20% chance based on soft world corruption */
		<span class="lewd">Strange shipments are coming in today.</span> The crew that normally handles them asked for help with the overflow. A manager announces that the overtime rate is raised from 150% to 200% for the day.
		<<set $docks.dayType to "lewd">>
	<<else>> /* remaining chance, 50-70% */
		The usual number of ships are coming through the docks today.
		<<set $docks.dayType to "normal">>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<dockoptions>>

/* The following passages are a workaround to allow widgets to be called from links */
:: Docks Leave
<<effects>>
<<dockleave>>

:: Docks Options
<<effects>>
<<dockoptions>>

:: Docks Lunch
<<effects>>
<<docklunchoptions>>

/* In the Docks Work passage, $phase determines action: 0 is working, 1 is slacking  */
:: Docks Work
<<set $outside to 1>><<effects>>

<<if $arousal gte $arousalmax>>
	<<orgasmLocation "docks">>
<</if>>

<<if $phase is 0>>
	당신은 열심히 일한다.
	<<if $docks.dayType is "busy">>
		끔찍하게 피곤하다.
		<<physique 9>>
	<<elseif $docks.dayType is "slow">>
		a slow day, leaving plenty of time to take breaks when you're not needed.
		<<physique 3>>
	<<elseif $docks.dayType is "lewd">>
		tiring, and you feel strangely heated.
		<<physique 6>>
	<<else>>
		꽤 피곤하다.
		<<physique 6>>
	<</if>>

	<<if $upperwetstage gte 3 or $lowerwetstage gte 3>>
		<br><br>
		You feel the other dockers ogling your body through your wet clothing.
		<<gstress>><<garousal>><<stress 6>><<arousal 600>>
	<</if>>
<<elseif $phase is 1>>
	<<if $docks.dayType is "lewd">>
		You try to avoid handling the unusual cargo.
	<<else>>
		당신은 가능한 한 일을 적게 한다.
	<</if>>
	<<set _daily_slacked to ($docks.dailyHours.shift.slacked + $docks.dailyHours.overtime.slacked)>>
	<<if $docks.dayType is "slow">>
		Your colleagues <span class="teal">don't mind you slacking today.</span>
	<<else>>
		<<if $docks.status gte 80>>
			<<if _daily_slacked is 1>>
				Your colleagues <span class="green">don't mind.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 2>>
				Your colleagues <span class="lblue">cover for you.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 3>>
				Your colleagues <span class="blue">let it slide.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 4>>
				Your colleagues <span class="purple">are getting impatient.</span>
			<<elseif $docks.dayType is "busy">>
				Your colleagues <span class="red">are angry that you're not helping on a busy day.</span><<dockstatus -2>><<llcool>>
			<<else>>
				동료들은 <span class="red">당신에 대해 불평한다.</span><<dockstatus -1>><<lcool>>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $docks.status gte 60>>
			<<if _daily_slacked is 1>>
				Your colleagues <span class="lblue">cover for you.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 2>>
				Your colleagues <span class="blue">let it slide.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 3>>
				Your colleagues <span class="purple">are getting impatient.</span>
			<<elseif $docks.dayType is "busy">>
				Your colleagues <span class="red">are angry that you're not helping on a busy day.</span><<dockstatus -2>><<llcool>>
			<<else>>
				동료들은 <span class="red">당신에 대해 불평한다.</span><<dockstatus -1>><<lcool>>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $docks.status gte 40>>
			<<if _daily_slacked is 1>>
				Your colleagues <span class="blue">let it slide.</span>
			<<elseif _daily_slacked is 2>>
				Your colleagues <span class="purple">are getting impatient.</span>
			<<elseif $docks.dayType is "busy">>
				Your colleagues <span class="red">are angry that you're not helping on a busy day.</span><<dockstatus -2>><<llcool>>
			<<else>>
				동료들은 <span class="red">당신에 대해 불평한다.</span><<dockstatus -1>><<lcool>>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $docks.status gte 20>>
			<<if _daily_slacked is 1>>
				Your colleagues <span class="purple">are getting impatient.</span>
